channel.description:
Hey, I've been added on my server the Skillcape Emotes. I did and complied server side: No errors. But when I complie class 20, I get this error: :confused: [img]http://img693.imageshack.us/img693/7961/sinttulouim.png[/img] Whats wrong?
--Edit-- I think it must go to client help. I posted it yesterday, but no1 tells me why i got this error, so I figured that it posted on wrong section. :|

item.title: Whats Wrong?
item.dc:creator: @CoonHunter CoonHunter
item.description:
@CoonHunter wrote:

duhelis:

Read: Code to Large…

He obviously does not know what is wrong when it says that, so please, help or don’t say anything.

@TOPIC - The method is too large itself. Methods can only be (last time I herd) 64KB is size. You have too much data in the method, you will need to create a copy of the method if you don’t want to delete things. Otherwise, you will need to delete some emotes from it.

P.S - This goes in the client help section, not server-help
